# Phase 4 — Privilege Escalation

## Overview
Starting from svc-mssql credentials obtained in Phase 2,
this phase demonstrates a full privilege escalation path
to Domain Admin using three chained techniques:
ACL discovery via BloodHound, WriteDACL abuse via dacledit.py,
and DCSync credential dumping via secretsdump.py.
No GUI access, no RDP, no admin rights required at any step.

