| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Tactic | Privilege Escalation, Defense Evasion, Persistence |
| Technique | T1078.002 — Valid Accounts: Domain Accounts |
| Technique | T1003.006 — OS Credential Dumping: DCSync |
